{"tid":1652001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府新聞處：警方8月向各部門借車作後勤","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:13:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbbe17a125834178648345a89f98ace6d213951","tid":1652001,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"反修訂《逃犯條例》風波至今已有4個月，今日（13日）全港多區有大批示威者堵路及破壞，有示威者下午於屯門破壞輕鐵石排站設施時，有警員乘坐一輛印有康文署標誌的白色客貨車到場，其後下車制服多人。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞處晚上8時許回覆本報查詢表示，警務處在今年8月透過政府物流服務署，向各部門要求借用政府車輛，以作後勤服務之用；並證實上述於屯門出現的車輛是其中一輛借出的車輛，原為康文署擁有，現由警方全權使用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191013/s00001/1570972436634/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191013%2Fs00001%2F1570972436634%2F&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=a726b576\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191013%2Fs00001%2F1570972436634%2F&h=5b67c24d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191013/s00001/1570972436634/</a>"},{"pid":"2fadbc66bc30a0a68c7f029e6f9e0a4e69518002","tid":1652001,"uid":219010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"老豆搵車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dde7f02db3eba3814ccb3f1e94f6924eb41d753","tid":1652001,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75b2d2e15845441a0d4f2ed36f89f3ce8a3f435","tid":1652001,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d39703a423badc88ef686a1d95c34301d851d3b","tid":1652001,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:04:05.000Z","